lightning
------------------------------------------
GNU lightning is a library to aid in making portable programs that compiles
assembly code at run time.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.3.6-1
  liblightning-devel-2.2.0-1bl1
  liblightning2-2.2.0-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.9.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.39-1
  cygport-0.35.4-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  libtool-2.4.7-1
  make-4.4-1

Canonical website:
  https://www.gnu.org/software/lightning/

Canonical download:
  mirror://gnu/lightning/lightning-2.2.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack lightning-2.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./lightning-2.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/lightning-2.2.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/lightning-2.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblightning2-2.2.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblightning-devel-2.2.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(lightning)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/lightning.README
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/README
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/THANKS
  /usr/share/doc/lightning/TODO

(liblightning2)
  /usr/bin/cyglightning-2.dll

(liblightning-devel)
  /usr/include/lightning.h
  /usr/include/lightning/jit_x86.h
  /usr/lib/liblightning.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/lightning.pc
  /usr/share/info/lightning.info.gz

